  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study, is to study the uptake of the pharmaceutical antifungal miconazole
      when used as a vaginal suppository in young women. The investigators want to know if the
      uptake is big enough to cause a biological effect (effect on CYP1A2 and CYP3A4 activity).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
